reclaim a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">child</ENAMEX> from adoptive <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">parents</ENAMEX>. You see it when <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">opponents</ENAMEX> of
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">cross</ENAMEX>-ethnic adoption argue--as in a <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">New York Times</ENAMEX> op-ed piece a few
