<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">every year</TIMEX> around <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Christmas</TIMEX>, when <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX> pay lip service to the idea of
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">universal</ENAMEX> brotherhood but believe in their hearts that it's ridiculous, that
