selection" during evolution. A greatly oversimplified textbook example: <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">Two</NUMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">million</ENAMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">years ago</TIMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> hominids, Loveless Bob and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Loving Bob</ENAMEX>, stand on <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX>
