<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Misconception No. 2</ENAMEX>: <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">People</ENAMEX> are smart--or,
at least, they are smart <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Darwinian</ENAMEX> robots . Darwinian theory does posit that
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">homo sapiens</ENAMEX> were "designed" to get their <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">genes</ENAMEX> into the next generation, but
not that they were designed to do so consciously and rationally. As surrogate
